Subject: [PATCH] verify_token_counts: add --counts-only mode and size_tier

Make the count-only path the recommended workflow. Skip the full-prompt
provider calls when no benchmark report is supplied, since those calls
are only meaningful for validating an existing run. Also classify each
case into a probe / signal / scaling tier based on the reported tokens
so readers of the printed table can interpret deltas appropriately.

